## REST API

### Auth

* POST `/register`
* POST `/login`
* GET `/profile`

### Projects

* GET `/projects`
* POST `/projects`
* PUT `/projects/:id`
* DELETE `/projects/:id`

### Tasks

* GET `/tasks`
* POST `/tasks`
* PUT `/tasks/:id`
* DELETE `/tasks/:id`

### Notifications

* GET `/notifications`
* PUT `/notifications/:id/read`

